{"tid":1392008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（超合作運動）渣車既巴絲入","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:21:22.000Z","uid":275380,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"338f84bf16e83db11955803ad05e403a2671fc3f","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"小弟係長期CD-ROM，最近先開AC, 不喜勿插<br />\n<br />\n相信大家渣車都成日遇過，啲工程撚成日封路（TTA, Temporary traffic Arrangement)  ，唔係封快線就封慢線，<br />\n成日Ｄ行車線就三收二，二收一，有啲人就話阻路可恥乜乜乜，拿，路爛就要整返好，岩既。<br />\n但有無發現黎黎去去，做路既都係果幾間公司，例如：昭hing,  Wai金, 順Yuen 等等。<br />\n<br />\n呢Ｄ公司既老細都好多公職架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如Wellcome既就係政協，順Yuen就係中華總商會會董咁<br />\n大家都愛國愛港，不用分得那麼細，拆爛河痴百歲磚咁叻叻，梗係想佢再做好Ｄ啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先封路呢，就要根據一本野，叫<strong>道路工程的照明、標誌及防護工作守則</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GP4j31t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGP4j31t.jpg&h=4f806f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications_and_publicity%2Fpublications%2Ftechnical_document%2Fcode_of_practice%2Findex.html&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGBmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=984bdc79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁呢本野就詳細講述左封路既程序，點封法，燈，筒既間距咁<br />\n<br />\n當渣車可見到有封路前首先就係可以見到掘路，收窄同封link<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ow4Hf3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOw4Hf3B.jpg&h=5e4d3562&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n通常於快速公路見到呢三款牌，下方都有＂接近危險地點標誌的距離字牌＂如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqcYyUW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqcYyUW.png&h=10c8c902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常呢Ｄ標誌牌都係寫住300,200,100或600,400,200<br />\n跟住再行前就會見到開始封路，呢啲路牌九成都會綁係路燈度，而路燈既間距為 30-40m，計計ＬＣＭ定ＨＣＦ就知每塊牌既間距係無可能係岩。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係掘路，收窄同封link既實際樣子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2OdnV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2OdnV1.jpg&h=3314236a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左距離字牌就到封路既斜頭，公路既車速限制有唔同既長度，而呢個位置好大機會唔夠長，而道路工程終止牌則 經常被消失或缺左一邊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>楔形路段</strong>（斜頭）現實既樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZXQ9Ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZXQ9Ed.jpg&h=8936e3bc&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n參考表，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">封路愈寬，斜頭愈長，衰梗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBYQqO3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBYQqO3.jpg&h=752c0305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: orange;\">雪糕筒間距</span>又係一個好有趣既切入位<br />\n<br />\n楔形路段及臨時改道路線邊緣&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2米&mdash;</span></strong><br />\n一般的<span style=\"font-size: large;\">楔形引入路段</span></span>，或在並非沿著現有行車綫邊緣的臨時改道行車綫兩旁。<br />\n1米&mdash;<br />\n在實施交通管制措施時成45度角的楔形引入路段，或在楔形引出路段。<br />\n1米&mdash;<br />\n佔用車路並與車路毗鄰的臨時行人路邊緣。<br />\n沿著現有行車綫的邊緣&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3米</span></span>&mdash;在車速限制每小時最高不超過<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">50</span></span>公里的路上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9米</span></span></span>&mdash;在車速限制每小時<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">70公里至80公里</span></span>的路上，或在車速限制超過每小時80公里的道路的急彎及近<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連接路之處。</span></span>（當道路危險警告燈需要根據第4.35段的規定放置時，警告燈須放置在用作標示邊界的圓筒中間，並須安裝在附加的圓筒上，令道路使用者可每隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.5米</span></span>看到一個圓筒，並每隔一個圓筒看到一盞警告燈。）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">18米</span></span>&mdash;在車速限制<span style=\"color: violet;\">超過每小時80公里</span>的道路或快速公路，<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但在急彎或近連接路的道路</span></span>除外。（當道路危險警告燈需要根據第4.35段的規定放置時，警告燈須放置在用作標示邊界的圓筒中間，並須安裝在附加的圓筒上，令道路使用者可每隔<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">9米</span></span>看到一個圓筒，並可每隔一個圓筒看到一盞警告燈。）<br />\n<br />\n因為夜晚會加閃燈所以間距會唔同左，呢個有Ｄ複雜同煩，即係咁：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFnd8da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFnd8da.jpg&h=b629ae04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔夠囉</span><br />\n<br />\n所以如果封路封得衰係真係會死人架，google 一下偉kim就知真係修橋補路無屍骸，為人為己，如果發現佢封路封到有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即時危險</span></span>，例如<strong>灣心起斜頭</strong>，Ｄ箭咀燈牌唔識閃或<strong>覺得</strong>暗，閃燈唔夠閃等等<br />\n可以致電９９９處理（如果打得通的話），清淅報出路段方向位置，記緊拎報案篇號跟進，相信<span style=\"color: pink;\">交通部</span>會很<span style=\"font-size: large;\">感激你的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係非緊急而又想我地既愛國愛港人士再做好啲既<br />\n可用１８２３ａｐｐ，夠熟ＣＯＰ可以直接打去傾計，暫時１８２３係呢啲層面仲係有效既。由於封路都幾複雜，所以小弟做個簡單既 template，大家可以copy低做demo，附件是旦cap張影到條封路既車cam相，入晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係demo：<br />\n<br />\n本人支持政府依法施政，在XXXX年XX月XX日，於XX公路近XXX段往XX方向，發現有工程在公路上，不知道是什麼部門的，但啲工程車寫住 昭hing/ Wai金/ 順Yuen 咁，我經過時見到<br />\n<br />\n自選可多項：<br />\n&mdash; 雪糕筒好疏，明明xx km應該要 X米一個既 (透露自己係識既,明玩, 你咪試下唔跟進囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n&mdash; 斜頭雪糕筒好疏／唔夠密，明明。。。<br />\n&mdash; 閃燈好暗／閃燈唔迫識閃／無閃燈<br />\n&mdash; 箭咀燈唔識著／唔識閃／唔夠光／唔係箭咀<br />\n&mdash; （如有，不過成日發生）工程車於封路內突然駛出，嚇到其他駕駛者（１８２３／９９９）<br />\n&mdash; Ｄ指示牌擺度錯晒，誤導駕駛者，咁攪法真係好危險！<br />\n&mdash; Ｄ人係封路做野唔戴安全帽／反光衣（如有）<br />\n&mdash; 剪草Ｄ碎彈晒出行車線<br />\n&mdash; 阻路可恥阻住我去返工<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"b1e33f6b16dc503d446532da7e090605b09bc499","tid":1392008,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGBmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=82ffb21a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"53bf372519cd4e4b793e98e9a38f4282080f744b","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"我要飲食"},{"pid":"ca2b0f80eea26beb92749e4ac83421433a644ba7","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"e69c1df2c642e4564782d56669dd5e72f5e02d8c","tid":1392008,"uid":36095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"重發?"},{"pid":"75d876c6231a62e383b90b655fe18eabed29565b","tid":1392008,"uid":229954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"23a44f780e1e50a2642cbac21bc6df01e1a93c95","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e69c1df2c642e4564782d56669dd5e72f5e02d8c","tid":1392008,"uid":36095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"重發?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:28:21.000Z","msg":"朋友話時事台岩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec87d1b549c657c17ef4328dbcc9f15d17b592d","tid":1392008,"uid":159002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"[拋磚引玉] 外國出手不是夢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a16ef01c40f16897d45d654680b979b9adb02e9","tid":1392008,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"},{"pid":"3cbc483d93edabdf056d5668c7efdc43cfe93d9b","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a16ef01c40f16897d45d654680b979b9adb02e9","tid":1392008,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"Sorry 1999"},{"pid":"ee4fe85d0eff46ef8534c27097bb0c63c43d5fe2","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a16ef01c40f16897d45d654680b979b9adb02e9","tid":1392008,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"邊 part唔明我可試下解說下"},{"pid":"d8194c76b16f2cc4c6e122dae142b048ae6f7a1a","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"其實999之後可以再1823<br />\n因999係警察跟進<br />\n而1823就會落左封路果個deptment再入9 contractor<br />\n<br />\nWhy not both"},{"pid":"78f010eb1fb687611a97c6b681233bc27474baf8","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"bc30725bb5e3216f087e9813955d61b16f6256b2","tid":1392008,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:33:01.000Z","msg":"我要飲食"},{"pid":"5cdc174fa532ec1ccc3af3df559b68c66dd0e602","tid":1392008,"uid